        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, I want to celebrate not just your achievement, but the incredible journey that brought you here.", "Every challenge you faced became a stepping stone, every setback became a setup for a comeback.", "You turned obstacles into opportunities and pressure into power.", "You refused to let circumstances define your potential or limit your possibilities.", "Your achievement today is proof that persistence and character always pay off.", "I'm celebrating the warrior spirit that carried you through every difficulty to this moment."] },
        { lines: ["{{specialMemory}} was a preview of the greatness I'm celebrating in you today, {{receiverName}}.", "That moment revealed your capacity for excellence even when the stakes were high.", "You showed me then what you could do when you combined talent with determination.", "Today's achievement is the full flowering of the potential I glimpsed in that special moment.", "I'm grateful for both that memory and this new milestone you've reached.", "You've proven that great moments are not accidents—they're the result of consistent character and commitment."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the ripple effects your achievement will have on everyone around you, {{receiverName}}.", "You've shown others that their dreams are possible and their goals are achievable.", "You've proven that excellence is not reserved for a select few but available to anyone willing to pursue it.", "Your success gives permission for others to believe in their own potential.", "You've become a beacon of possibility in a world that often discourages big dreams.", "I'm celebrating not just what you've done, but what you've inspired others to believe they can do."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement reflects the values that have guided you throughout your life, {{receiverName}}.", "You've shown that integrity and excellence can coexist, that you don't have to compromise character to achieve success.", "You've proven that doing the right thing and doing things right leads to meaningful outcomes.", "Your success has been earned honestly through authentic effort and genuine merit.", "I'm celebrating not just the achievement, but the honorable way you've pursued it.", "You've shown that true success is about who you become in the process of achieving your goals."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the doors this achievement opens for your future, {{receiverName}}.", "This success creates momentum that will carry you to even greater heights.", "You've established yourself as someone capable of exceptional things.", "This achievement becomes a foundation for everything that follows in your life.", "I'm excited about the opportunities this will create and the possibilities it will unlock.", "I'm celebrating not just where you are today, but where this achievement will take you tomorrow."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement is a testament to the power of believing in yourself when others doubted, {{receiverName}}.", "You stayed committed to your vision even when the path was unclear or difficult.", "You maintained faith in your abilities when circumstances suggested you should give up.", "You persevered through seasons when success seemed impossible or distant.", "Your achievement today validates every moment of faith you maintained in yourself.", "I'm celebrating the courage it took to believe in yourself and the wisdom of that belief."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the unique gifts and talents that made this achievement possible, {{receiverName}}.", "You have a rare combination of skills, character, and vision that sets you apart.", "You see possibilities where others see problems and solutions where others see obstacles.", "Your natural abilities, combined with your work ethic, create something truly special.", "I'm grateful to witness the full expression of your gifts through this achievement.", "You've shown what happens when talent meets opportunity and preparation meets purpose."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement proves that you're exactly where you're supposed to be, doing exactly what you're meant to do, {{receiverName}}.", "This success feels natural and right because it aligns with your purpose and calling.", "You've found your lane and run your race with excellence and authenticity.", "This achievement is not just a goal reached—it's a destiny fulfilled.", "I'm celebrating the beautiful alignment of your gifts, your passion, and your purpose.", "You've shown what's possible when someone discovers their true calling and pursues it with everything they have."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the growth and transformation that this achievement represents in your life, {{receiverName}}.", "You've become someone capable of things you might not have imagined when you started this journey.", "This success has revealed capacities and strengths you might not have known you possessed.", "You've expanded your sense of what's possible and elevated your standards for yourself.", "I'm celebrating not just the achievement, but the person you've become in the process of achieving it.", "Your success is beautiful because it reflects the best version of yourself."] },
        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, as I celebrate your achievement, I'm filled with gratitude for the privilege of being your brother.", "I get to witness firsthand the remarkable person you are and the incredible things you accomplish.", "I get to share in the joy of your successes and take pride in your achievements.", "I get to learn from your example and be inspired by your dedication and character.", "I get to celebrate milestones like this one and look forward to many more to come.", "Thank you for being someone worth celebrating and for allowing me to be part of your incredible journey."] },
        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, today I'm celebrating the perfect combination of preparation and opportunity that led to your success.", "You were ready when your moment came because you'd been preparing for it all along.", "Your achievement didn't happen by chance—it happened by choice and commitment.", "You created your own opportunities through consistent effort and unwavering dedication.", "I'm celebrating the years of unseen work that made today's visible success possible.", "You've proven that luck is what happens when preparation meets opportunity."] },
        { lines: ["{{specialMemory}} perfectly illustrates the qualities that made today's achievement inevitable, {{receiverName}}.", "That moment showed me your heart, your determination, and your refusal to settle for less than your best.", "I saw then what I'm celebrating now—your capacity for greatness when it matters most.", "That memory and this moment are connected by the consistent character you've shown throughout your life.", "I'm grateful for every memory that has revealed your true potential.", "Today's achievement is the natural result of the person you've always been."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the courage it took to pursue something meaningful rather than settling for something easy, {{receiverName}}.", "You chose the challenging path because it led to something worthwhile.", "You rejected mediocrity in favor of excellence, comfort in favor of growth.", "You took risks and faced uncertainty because you believed in something greater.", "Your achievement today validates every brave choice you made along the way.", "I'm celebrating not just the outcome, but the courage that made it possible."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement represents the triumph of persistence over every obstacle that tried to stop you, {{receiverName}}.", "You faced setbacks and kept moving forward, encountered resistance and pushed through.", "You met challenges with creativity and problems with solutions.", "You refused to let temporary failures become permanent defeats.", "Your success today is evidence that persistence always pays off for those who refuse to quit.", "I'm celebrating your unbreakable spirit and your unwavering determination."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the way your achievement honors everyone who believed in you and supported your dreams, {{receiverName}}.", "Your success validates the faith that family and friends placed in your potential.", "You've justified every investment of time, energy, and emotion that people made in your future.", "Your achievement repays the confidence that others showed when they encouraged you to pursue your goals.", "I'm grateful to be among those who believed in you from the beginning.", "You've proven that our belief was well-founded and our support was worthwhile."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement demonstrates that excellence is not about perfection—it's about persistence, {{receiverName}}.", "You didn't have to be perfect to achieve something extraordinary.", "You just had to be persistent, dedicated, and willing to learn and grow.", "Your success shows that ordinary people can achieve extraordinary things through sustained effort.", "I'm celebrating the human triumph that your achievement represents.", "You've proven that greatness is accessible to anyone willing to pursue it with commitment and character."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the positive impact your achievement will have on the next generation, {{receiverName}}.", "Young people who know your story will see what's possible when someone commits to excellence.", "They'll learn from your example that dreams can become reality through hard work and dedication.", "Your success becomes part of their roadmap for pursuing their own meaningful goals.", "I'm grateful that your achievement creates inspiration for others to follow.", "You've become a living example of what's possible when someone refuses to give up on their potential."] },
        { lines: ["Your achievement proves that investing in yourself is always worthwhile, {{receiverName}}.", "Every hour of practice, every moment of study, every sacrifice you made has paid dividends.", "You believed in your own potential enough to invest time and energy in developing it.", "Your success today is the return on that investment, and it was worth every bit of effort.", "I'm celebrating not just the achievement, but the wisdom you showed in believing you were worth the investment.", "You've proven that the best investment anyone can make is in their own growth and development."] },
        { lines: ["I'm celebrating the alignment between your achievement and your character, {{receiverName}}.", "Your success feels right because it matches who you are and what you represent.", "You've achieved something meaningful in a way that honors your values and principles.", "Your accomplishment enhances your character rather than contradicting it.", "I'm grateful that your achievement reflects the best of who you are.", "You've shown that true success is about becoming the kind of person who naturally achieves worthwhile things."] },
        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, as I celebrate your achievement, I'm also celebrating our relationship and what it means to me.", "Having a brother like you makes me proud, makes me better, and makes me grateful every day.", "Your success brings joy to my life because your happiness and fulfillment matter deeply to me.", "I'm honored to share in your victories and privileged to call you my brother.", "Your achievement is cause for celebration not just because of what you've accomplished, but because of who accomplished it.", "Here's to your success, to our bond, and to many more reasons to celebrate in the years ahead."] }
